WEBVTT

00:01.534 --> 00:05.664
<i>Theorizing that one could time travel
within his own lifetime,</i>

00:05.739 --> 00:08.674
<i>Dr. Sam Beckett stepped
into the Quantum Leap accelerator...</i>

00:08.742 --> 00:10.733
<i>and vanished.</i>

00:16.082 --> 00:19.449
<i>He awoke to find himself
trapped in the past,</i>

00:19.519 --> 00:21.544
<i>facing mirror images
that were not his own...</i>

00:21.621 --> 00:26.854
<i>and driven by an unknown force
to change history for the better.</i>

00:26.926 --> 00:32.192
<i>His only guide on this journey is Al,
an observer from his own time,</i>

00:32.265 --> 00:36.634
<i>who appears in the form of a hologram
that only Sam can see and hear.</i>

00:36.703 --> 00:41.072
<i>And so, Dr. Beckett finds himself
leaping from life to life,</i>

00:42.442 --> 00:44.876
<i>striving to put right
what once went wrong...</i>

00:44.944 --> 00:47.344
<i>and hoping each time
that his next leap...</i>

00:47.414 --> 00:49.405
<i>will be the leap home.</i>

00:52.152 --> 00:54.882
<i>Dad.! Dad, you're home.!
Daddy.! Daddy.! You're here.!</i>

00:54.954 --> 00:57.946
Well, it's about time.
Mmm.

00:58.024 --> 01:02.051
<i>Arriving passenger Martin Elroy,
please report to the courtesy desk.</i>

01:02.128 --> 01:04.119
- Martin Elroy.
- What's that about?

01:04.197 --> 01:06.597
What's what about?
They just paged you.

01:06.666 --> 01:11.160
Oh. Well, I guess I was so excited to
see everybody, I didn't hear it. Oh!

01:11.237 --> 01:15.173
Well, we'll get your bags and meet you
at the curb. But don't take too long.

01:15.241 --> 01:19.735
I've got a pot roast in the oven
and somethin' special for dessert.

01:20.747 --> 01:23.477
<i>Come on.
Welcome back, Daddy.</i>

01:23.550 --> 01:28.112
<i>Attention, please. This is the final
boarding call for flight 203 to Miami.</i>

01:28.188 --> 01:32.557
<i>Look at this.</i>

01:32.625 --> 01:35.116
Just a moment, please.
You, uh-

01:42.035 --> 01:45.266
Kids?
Yea, Dad!

01:45.338 --> 01:48.273
Oh, Daddy! Oh!
I missed you, Daddy! Mmm!

01:48.341 --> 01:50.332
<i>Surprise.!
I missed you, Daddy.</i>

01:50.410 --> 01:52.344
Oh, boy.

